{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Propagates the note names of last clicked track to all selected tracks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The script will open a dialog box in which the user can:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab confirm or change the source track, and\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab select whether all existing note names in the selected tracks should be removed.\sa180\par}
}

